Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Birthday cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:07.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cakes used to celebrate birthdays,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:11.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,traditionally topped with a number of candles\Nequal to your age, which are then lit on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:16.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}But this time, that fire gets mishandled...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.51,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A canvas stained black with crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:23.15,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}With brilliant detective skills, its color is changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:27.13,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Everyone's curious about first loves.\NSour feelings spark up a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.95,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:25.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for offering to clean Shin'ichi's house, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem! We have nothing to do anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't decide these things on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:36.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But it {\i1}will{\i0} turn into a ghost house if we don't clean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:44.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi must be happy to have such a thoughtful girlfriend as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're off, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:08.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of cleaning\Nthe entire house, are you, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's do as much as we can for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:15.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Does that mean we're going to clean all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} get stuck\Ncleaning Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on such a nice Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just ignored it,\Nyet you went and got Doc's spare key!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:40.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I just figured the place was covered in dust
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that it'd be hard to clean alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sonoko. You should dust\Nthe bookcases before sweeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:52.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they say, you should clean from the top down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:59.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you're supposed to follow\Nthe tiles when sweeping the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like such an old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls these days are supposed\Nto be crazy about catching men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:10.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and experiencing pure love, first love, and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet here I am, getting covered\Nin dust for that mystery dweeb...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm oh-so-pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So sorry for the trouble, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Speaking of first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:24.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:29.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose Shin'ichi's first love was like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:29.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've had a love or two by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:40.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. He's super-dull in the head\Nwhen it comes to things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:46.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, given his hot mother,\Nit was probably a TV idol, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:52.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you've always\Nbeen together since you were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, you're thoughtful {\i1}and{\i0} strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:01.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, maybe {\i1}you're{\i0} his first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:01.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:08.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! We only played\Ntogether when we were kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then there's your precedent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:16.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! Don't make stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:25.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Your bashfulness says\Notherwise, Girl of Twenty Faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Sonoko! Before I get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb! It's obviously Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, I kind of doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he ring the doorbell to his own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably heard about us from\Nthe doc and wants to surprise us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's {\i1}not{\i0} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Shin'ichi didn't say\Nanything about coming home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so embarrassed about? Hurry and see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your first love prince, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:02.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?! Isn't she...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, are you Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:15.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:23.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was student body president\Nduring our first year of middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know! Asami Uchida-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:26.84,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami Uchida (18)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 1st Year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:32.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. So Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has been away\Nfor a while on some cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:35.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I always got the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:39.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it's almost like I've asked you to clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem at all! I had nothing else to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}. Why did\Nyou want to see Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:50.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends in the university's mystery\Nclub are going to rent a lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and hold a birthday party for me this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to invite Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:03.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as he's a great detective\Nand an old soccer club teammate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I sent the letter quite a while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say anything before he left home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:19.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I was sure he would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:23.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he forgot about that\Nconfession four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:28.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess I can't blame him for forgetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:34.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First loves are bound to fade away with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,F-First love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:43.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She was Shin'ichi's first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it. It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was talking about it\Nour first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly a first-year boy\Nmade a pass at Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:58.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that daredevil was actually Shin'ichi Kudo, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:02.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like that. It was an actual confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:12.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shin'ichi-{\i1}niichan{\i0} won't go, why not ask someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:20.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've solved a few cases ourselves, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:26.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! We might be able to\Ncatch some lively Tohto boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think my male friends would\Nlove having high school girls attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:36.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if you invite us, there's no\Nquestion that he'll come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sonoko! You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:43.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! The great detective who needs no introduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A get-together of Tohto\NUniversity's mystery study club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow you to go to a\Nsleepover without any real adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're invited too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:09:00.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy! I don't have time to mess with stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As a great detective,\Nyou can't relax on a weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:17.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But for the mystery study club,\NKogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is almost like a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:22.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How they'd all like to hear from the peerless detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention all the pretty girls who'll be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,including Asami Uchida-{\i1}sempai{\i0},\Nwho holds the title of Miss Tohto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Tohto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:35.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're busy, we'll accept that we can't go either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:40.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure I can somehow\Nrearrange my busy schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to go with you as your chaperone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I wouldn't want to disappoint\Nall the promising youngsters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:49.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of this mystery study club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What a predictable personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Miss Tohto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is the lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:16.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus stop is here, so we go up and right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:23.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Over there? Miss Tohto isn't too far now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm gonna get me a Tohto boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:39.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...being able to talk and drink\Nwith the young minds of Tohto U!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:43.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, you're all\Ngood-looking boys and pretty girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:52.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Manabu Sawai (22)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 4th Year\NPresident of Mystery Study Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I'd expect from a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:52.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to control\Npeople's hearts with words alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:57.74,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoko Hayasaka (21)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 4th Year\NV.P. of Mystery Study Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:57.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you sure you're not referring\Nto yourself, playboy Sawai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:02.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you made a 1st-year\Ngirl cry just recently, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:04.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Chika Miyazaki (19)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 2nd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:04.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibahisa Noguchi (20)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 2nd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:04.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:08.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! This is Asami's birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to put me on trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And it's also a celebration party
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the "Newcomer Award"\Nher novel won the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too bad, Morimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:22.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you made it to the final selection, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:28.35,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshinobu Morimoto (22)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 3rd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:28.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to Asami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, our\Ndepartment's most promising writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:35.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to her pair in the Literature\NDepartment's tennis tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus she was named Miss Tohto as a freshman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even make it through the preliminary round...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really admire her. She can do\Neverything, but doesn't act conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's also an incredible cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, where is her lemon pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She and Ran are baking it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:56.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said she was going\Nto make one and bring it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I've been looking forward to this!\N- Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sloppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really make this, Asami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:11.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did. It was my first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your pie, Asami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:16.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally forgot to bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:21.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she would make one for me, so I asked her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Why're you making stuff you don't know how to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Save your criticism\Nuntil after you've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little fragrant, but it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Me too!\N- Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:56.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It looks iffy, but tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? With cooking, substance is what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:08.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you eat it, you can't tell\Nwhat it looks like anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:19.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've solved every case 100% of the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you solved the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I was the one who solved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a pretty cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went all the way to Ginza to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find some matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's okay. I borrowed Sawai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:47.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any age, watching birthday\Ncandles being lit is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, only until you're 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:58.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Once you're over 20,\Nyou start to hate each extra candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:08.55,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Congratulations.\NI pray for even greater future success.\NTohto Literature Prof. Masao Takamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right at midnight, as promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's good we got a lodge with a fax machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} sent it, Asami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. What should we do with the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we supposed to go to the\Nkaraoke place by the station next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I already made reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:35.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's save the cake for tomorrow\Nand go do karaoke ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:39.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nothing else we can do. Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:51.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}"Karaoke Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}ahh nazo ga tokete-yuku\N{\c\3c}Ahh, the mystery begins to unravel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:56.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}nazo ga tokete-yuku...\N{\c\3c}The mystery begins to unravel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:01.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, little boy. Want to sing Two-Mix with me next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'll go next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:14.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}negaigoto hitotsu-dake kanaete-kureru-nara\N{\c\3c}If I could have one wish granted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:22.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kizutsukeatta ai ga hajimaranai-you ni...\N{\c\3c}It would be that our love wouldn't make us both hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the glum look?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! I'm not glum at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I guess what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart and beautiful, a sports warrior and scholar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:27.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Considerate, popular, and #1 at everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking about Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! How could you tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:46.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}doushite futari wa deatta no?\N{\c\3c}How did they meet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:54.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kon'na ni sabishii yuuhi o miru nante\N{\c\3c}Looking at such a lonely sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:16:02.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}ki no ki'ita kotoba sagashite mo\N{\c\3c}Even as I try to find clever words
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\a7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}hanareta kokoro o tsunagu kotoba nakute\N{\c\3c}There are none to connect our distant hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:36.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm no match for her!" is written all over your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:40.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't blame Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} for falling for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She {\i1}was{\i0} the soccer club's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:51.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry about it!\NShe must've rejected him anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:53.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:59.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know Shin'ichi loves lemon pie, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it for the first time today from Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.69,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Eh? Shin'ichi loves lemon pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.19,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes! It's his favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:15.74,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I told everyone I'd make one\Nbecause I thought he'd come today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.70,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}so I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.49,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh? Shin'ichi does?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.46,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He loves this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:27.31,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}I can teach you how to make it if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:34.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows so much about Shin'ichi that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:36.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:47.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There are a lot fewer people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were taking so long in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ran off to the bathrooms by the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you have my cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some at the convenience store next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Noguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:07.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still walking around the train station to sober up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past 3:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should head back.\NWe left the place messy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tidy up and hit the hay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Is that a fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...our lodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:28.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:35.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0} is still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry to the lodge!\NWe might still make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the rental car key?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:50.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's the problem"?!\NThe lodge we rented is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\i1}Sempai{\i0}... {\i1}Sempai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:04.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Please be all right, Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Asami!\N- Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! It doesn't look like she fled outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me she's still asleep inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:26.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we call her on the phone?!\NShe was asleep in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! It's already burned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! There's no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:32.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use! There's no way inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:46.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Move that motorcycle!\NWe don't want its gasoline to ignite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the fire truck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My helmet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm coming, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Ran and Conan went inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,President Sawai followed them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}! Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! My daughter's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be in danger too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:30.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:42.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:53.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A hospital near the lodge.\NThey brought you here afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:07.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than a little carbon\Nmonoxide poisoning, she's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:11.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! She made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:14.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NYou're the one who saved her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:16.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:22.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all... I rushed inside without thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:26.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sawai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} led the way to safety after I found her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:32.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt relieved when I got outside,\Nbut things got blurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:35.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was amazing! You busted\Ninside with that helmet on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:40.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the firefighters said that\Nit wasn't smart to go into the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:42.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but wearing the helmet was the correct thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:46.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:51.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave it to me just as I was about to run inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I should put it on to protect\Nmy hair and face from the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} did? He's as strange a kid as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:09.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the fire started around 2:50?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:14.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. People in nearby lodges\Nsaid they saw smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:18.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought it was a bonfire at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:21.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you suspect it was arson?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The fire started in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:26.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This cake candle was probably the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It probably fell onto the floor while still lit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:39.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where it ignited the nearby\Nwrapping paper and curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you blow them out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:44.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! I did put them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:48.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped. We were\Nall in a hurry when we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I put them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:54.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the candle did burn down to its base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:58.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she didn't forget to put it out,\Nthere's one other possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:05.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility that Asami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} herself\Nlit the fire in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd! Why would she do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Sempai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:50.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:54.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've left while we were\Ngetting something to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:23:56.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was nearly burned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By one of you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:14.97,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Conan's Hint: Convenience Store
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:22.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Oh, right, Sonoko, who was your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:22.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:26.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Did you have so many that you can't think of just one?
